File:ex4a.cc
calculate the average and the
variance of values in an array
=========================================
Writen by: Michael Shriki, login = michaelshr

the program calculate the average and the variance of values in an array

Compile: g++ -Wall ex4a.cc –oex4a
Run: ex4a
Input: 	7 value to array;
            e.g. 1 2 3 4 5 6 7.

Output: the average and the variance of
values in the array
	    e.g. 4 4 

Run Time: O(n), when n is the number of values in an array 

