File:ex4b.cc
a program that finding the most common values in an array
=========================================
Writen by: Michael Shriki, id = 305599417, login = michaelshr

this program finding the most common values in an array

Compile: g++ -Wall ex4b.cc –oex4b
Run: ex4b
Input: 	10 value to array;
            e.g. 3 3 6 4 2 4 0 1 1 7.

Output: the most common value(s) in the array.
	e.g. 3
	     4
	     1

Run Time: O(n*m), when n is the number of values in an array 
and m is the number of valuse in the  counting array


