File:ex4c.cc
a program that finding a loop in an array and print the loop
=========================================
Writen by: Michael Shriki, id = 305599417, login = michaelshr

the program finding a loop in an array and print the loop

Compile: g++ -Wall ex4c.cc –oex4c
Run: ex4c
Input: 	10 values to array;
            e.g. 5 4 6 7 3 8 9 2 1 0

Output: the program print the first loop in the array and the first place
that the loop start from 
	    e.g. 0 5 8 1 4 3 7 2 6 9 0

Run Time: O(n), when n is the number of values in an array

